- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on using visual information to enhance speech in videos. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with audio processing and noise reduction. 
- cs.SI (Speech and Natural Language Processing) is another possible category as the paper deals with speech enhancement. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with processing multimedia data (video and audio). 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on natural language processing, but it could be relevant as the paper deals with speech processing.
